item.title: CVE-2021-20336|2024-08-03T17:37:24.019Z -- ibm -- tivoli%20netcool%2Fomnibus_gui
item.description: IBM Tivoli Netcool/OMNIbus_GUI 8.1.0 is vulnerable to stored cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session.
